body:

your ATM Card which you have paid a lot of money for and in return got
nothing has been brought to our office yesterday by the IMF. So you
are to come over here in our office to have your package free of
charge. Office is in Harrisburg when you get to Harrisburg i will give
you further directions, But if you won't be able to come to our office
here in Harrisburg you are free to tell me so that i can get an
officer available for the delivery of the fund to your nearest
airport.
